&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Government &amp;amp; Public Sector Engagement: &lt;/strong&gt;Serve as Sand’s primary liaison to government ministries, agencies, and public sector institutions, building trusted relationships that enable successful product adoption.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Policy &amp;amp; Strategic Alignment:&lt;/strong&gt; Ensure Sand’s solutions are designed and implemented in alignment with national strategies, sector policies, and long-term government priorities.&lt;/li&gt;
